title: [Warehouse, Erantok's Emporium]
description: A long narrow corridor runs the length of the cave and openings for partitioned areas are staggered at even distances.  The sound of items being moved echoes in the huge space, giving it a somewhat eery atmosphere, especially when the torch-like oil lamps flicker with an undetectable breeze.
paths: Obvious exits: north, east, south, west
